<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/t3-9116/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div>
<div class="tw-foot p"><div class="fn" id="fn1"><p>* names provided for illustration purposes</p></div></div></section><p>Drug strength information, if available, is populated in ds_stage and contains dosage or strength of active substance, total volume of liquid drug or number of actuations for dosed inhalers or applicators as well as box size (<a href="#t4-9116" class="usa-link">Table 4</a>). Units of measures are converted to those used by RxNorm (such as conversion of grams into milligrams) to simplify subsequent matching.</p>
