<div class="p text-right font-secondary"><a href="table/t4-9116/" class="usa-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open in a new tab</a></div></section><p>Finally, relationship_to_concept maps ingredient, brand, dose form, supplier and unit concepts to standard RxNorm coutnerparts or UCUM coutnerparts for units of measure. If no mappings exist, the attributes will be created as new standard attributes in RxNorm Extension (<a href="#t5-9116" class="usa-link">Table 5</a>).</p>
<section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="t5-9116"><h4 class="obj_head">Table 5.</h4>
